message.body: What are you doing this afternoon?
Bb! I'm working on shit at my house... What are you doing?!
Well I'm hanging out with Steph tonight but schlepping around until then
Also, I totally didn't see your texts the other day about cmon roots, or I would have come!
Oh sad :( yea I was bummed but no big. It was the day I was supposed to go to Nashville so I was low
Ok. I have to photograph the poster for love song later, but you can hang out while I Photoshop?!
So sorry, sweetie! I'm a goddam idiot.
No no no quit it bb. That sounds goood.have you eaten lunch?
Not really, I was just about to hop in the shower
Also, I literally have no money right now. In fact I have negative money
No worries, I thought maybe we could make aomething to eat? I have veggies
Oooo, that sounds good. I have some too... When do you want to come over?
I have to get ready and stuff, but then I can head over
Sweet. I shower now. See you laterz.
Do you want to go to upright eggs show and work the bad with me tomorrow night?
Work the what? I might have to go to Lauren drasler's show tomorrow night
I can see you from the bridge... Hah. I'm on a walk. Nice rust pants.
